      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "PAGE ONE NEWS (1) turned spotting a big start finishing fourth (30.28) last time in a Grade 4/5 at this track. Solid record here winning four races. Has ability and looks hard to stop. WEST ON COLE (2) was sent out long odds last time but rocketed out of the boxes with a fast early sectional and gave a sight before being swallowed up late, finishing a 5.5 lengths third (30.55) over 520m at this track. Expecting another good run. TIMMY TESLA (5) comes off an average performance last start when eighth at this track over 520m behind Iconic Guess (31.22) in a Free For All. Has ability and can measure up. PREMIUM STAR (8) is a last-start placegetter worth considering.",
